  77,44,"'in aladhin khafuu rabihim fi aldnya, wataquu eadhabah bamtthal awamrh wajtnab nwahyh, hum yawm alqiamat fi zilal al'ashjar alwarft waeuyun alma' aljaryt, wafawakih kathirat mimaa tashtahih 'anfusahum ytnemwn. yuqal lhm: kuluu 'aklana ldhydhana, washrabuu shrbana hnyyana; bsbb ma qadamtum fi aldunya min salih alaemal. 'iinaa bimithl dhlk aljaza' aleazim najzi 'ahl al'iihsan fi 'aemalahum wtaethm lna. hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm aljaza' walhisab wama fih min alnaeim waledhab"
  77,45,"'in aladhin khafuu rabihim fi aldnya, wataquu eadhabah bamtthal awamrh wajtnab nwahyh, hum yawm alqiamat fi zilal al'ashjar alwarft waeuyun alma' aljaryt, wafawakih kathirat mimaa tashtahih 'anfusahum ytnemwn. yuqal lhm: kuluu 'aklana ldhydhana, washrabuu shrbana hnyyana; bsbb ma qadamtum fi aldunya min salih alaemal. 'iinaa bimithl dhlk aljaza' aleazim najzi 'ahl al'iihsan fi 'aemalahum wtaethm lna. hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm aljaza' walhisab wama fih min alnaeim waledhab"
  77,46,"thm hddad allah alkafirin fqal: kuluu min ldhaydh aldnya, wastmteu bshhwatha alfanyt zmnana qlyla; 'iinakum mujrimun b'ishrakkm ballh"
  77,47,hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biawm alhisab waljza'
  77,48,"wa'iidha qil lhwla' almshrkyn: sllu llh, wakhsheu lh, la ykhshewn wala ysllun, bal ysrrun ealaa astkbarhm"
  77,49,"hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biayat allh, 'iin lam yuminuu bhdha alqran, fabi'ayi kitab wklam baedah ywmnwn? wahu almbyin likuli shy', alwadih fi hukmih wahkamh wakhbarh, almejz fi alfazh wmeanyh"
  77,50,"hlak waeadhab shadid yawm alqiamat lilmukadhibin biayat allh, 'iin lam yuminuu bhdha alqran, fabi'ayi kitab wklam baedah ywmnwn? wahu almbyin likuli shy', alwadih fi hukmih wahkamh wakhbarh, almejz fi alfazh wmeanyh"